Package: trace
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
 python3-wxgtk4.0,
 libngspice0
Recommends: trace-libraries, trace-demos
Description: AI-Native PCB Design Suite
 Trace is a modified version of the KiCad EDA software, enhanced with
 AI-native circuit design capabilities. It features schematic capture,
 integrated circuit simulation, printed circuit board (PCB) layout,
 3D rendering, and AI-powered design assistance.
 .
 Trace extends KiCad with:
 .
  * AI Circuit Assistant for natural language design
  * Intelligent component search and suggestions
  * Cloud integration for team collaboration
  * Enhanced workflow for modern hardware engineering
 .
 Trace is made up of several components:
 .
  * Trace project manager
  * Schematic editor
  * PCB editor
  * 3D viewer
  * Gerber viewer

Package: trace-dbgsym
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: trace (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Debug symbols for Trace
 Debug symbols for the Trace AI-native PCB design suite.
 Install this package if you need to debug Trace crashes.

Package: trace-demos
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: trace
Description: Trace demo projects
 Example projects for learning Trace PCB design.
 Includes various typical small use cases from simple through-hole
 designs to complex SMD projects with multiple layers.
